Refractory depression: mechanisms and evaluation of radically open dialectical 
behaviour therapy (RO-DBT) [REFRAMED]: protocol for randomised trial.

Lynch TR(1), Whalley B(2), Hempel RJ(1), Byford S(3), Clarke P(4), Clarke S(5), 
Kingdon D(6), O'Mahen H(7), Russell IT(8), Shearer J(9), Stanton M(10), Swales 
M(11), Watkins A(8), Remington B(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Psychology, University of Southampton, Southampton, UK.
