Lamotrigine versus inert placebo in the treatment of borderline personality 
disorder: study protocol for a randomized controlled trial and economic 
evaluation.

Crawford MJ(1), Sanatinia R(2), Barrett B(3), Byford S(4), Cunningham G(5), 
Gakhal K(6), Lawrence-Smith G(7), Leeson V(8), Lemonsky F(9), Lykomitrou G(10), 
